title: Jacklight (1995)
description:
Plot: A forbidden game. A tragic accident. Now, five friends must confront the past, themselves and a shocking secret.

I came across this film when doing a bit of research on IMDB. I enjoyed the acting and character development. Although this genre has been done many times, this particular one stood out for me as it struck a personal nerve. On one particular level, I can relate to what the characters in this film are dealing with. I lost a few good friends during my High School years. At each of my High School reunions since, our dead friends become a topic of deep discussion and reflection.

There is a good chance you'll enjoy this film on one level or another.


XviD Avi
